# Accessibility Standards

> **Related Rules**: See [Theme Customization](./theming.mdc), [Layout Module Standards](./layout-specific.mdc)

## ARIA Labels

- All interactive elements need appropriate ARIA labels
- Form validation errors need clear prompts
- Use semantic HTML elements

## Keyboard Navigation

- Keyboard navigation support (Tab, Enter, Esc, etc.)
- All interactive functions must be operable via keyboard
- Ensure correct focus management

## Visual Design

- Color contrast meets WCAG 2.1 AA standards (see [Theme Customization Standards](./theming.mdc))
- Images provide alternative text (alt text)
- Do not use color as the only means of conveying information

